Text: Hah!
Aghh...!

You know, you're more emotionally expressive than
you come across as.
...And what of it?
Nothing. Just saying what I'm thinking.

Fighting these lower-level opponents won't diminish
Sergey's power...!

If you also start saying everything you're thinking,
our conversations might become a little too real and
out of control.
...I'll scout the area. You keep a lookout.
Copy that.
...How can you fight without any purpose?
You asking me?
Yeah.
Well...

...Maybe because even without a clear sense of
purpose, I still manage to perform effectively...
Does that count as an answer?

It's not an answer, but if you achieved the rank of
instructor with that mindset, you must be quite
talented.
Who knows? it might just be a surprisingly easy job.
Would you say that in front of Lady Lambda?
Hmm... Knowing me, I might accidentally let it slip.

Even without a clear purpose, people still have to
go on living, don't they? So long as they don't plan
on ending their lives or experience hunger every
day.

Even if some were to argue that living like that is
as good as not living, I'd just tell them that that's
one way to look at it.

...Honestly, I envy you being able to think that
way.
Is that sarcasm? ...I guess not.

To continue living a life of responsibility,
reputation, and pride, even now that you're no
longer an aristocrat or a knight... That must be
tough.
*gasp*

...I suppose I'm just not adaptable enough to
discover a way of living beyond that, even
more so than I had realized.
Probably.
...Found them.
So, these are the boxes... There are six in total.

We'll secure this place until Lady Beta and Lady
Epsilon eliminate the Cult members inside the
hideout.
Copy that.
What the...?!
What's the matter?
This box... It seemed to move a little just now...

Move? Haha! Are you suggesting there's some kind of
creature inside?

...I'll inspect the contents. Please continue to
keep watch.

Alright. Just be careful. You never know if it might
bite.
...What in the world is in this
Aaah...aaahh...aaah...?!
O-Ohhh...aaahh...!
H-How?! How is this possible?! Aaaahhhhaaahhhh!!!

Quiet down! What're you yelling for?! They'll hear
you

How... How could such a thing...be allowed...?!
This is unforgiveable!

It's madness... How?! How...could they do such
a thing?!
No. 111! What's the matter?!
Aaaaahhhh...
What did you seeahh!?!
Wh-What the...?!

A possessed...infant...?! No... Do all these boxes
contain...

The Cult has been committing such atrocities...while
I lived my life obliviously...!
Unforgivable... Unforgivable... Aaaaaahhh...!
Tsk...! They're onto us. No. 111!
O-Ohhh...aaahh...!

Stand up, No.111! Are you going to let yourself just
get killed?!
No. 111! FIGHT!
Fight for these infants! FIIIIIGHT!
Aahhh!!!
AAAAHHHHHHHHHH!!!
